OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1777482354
OL,3,CTwo young women left with life-
OL,4,Cchanging injuries after crash
OL,6,FTwo young women have been left with
OL,7,Flife-changing injuries following a
OL,8,Fcollision on the A69 in Newcastle.
OL,10,FIt happened shortly before midnight on
OL,11,FTuesday night (28 April) at Lemington.
OL,13,FPolice have said it was reported that
OL,14,Fa white Peugeot 108 was travelling in
OL,15,Fthe wrong direction on the westbound
OL,16,Fcarriageway when it collided with a
OL,17,Fred Citroen Picasso.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
