OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1777482354
OL,3,CTwo young women left with life-
OL,4,Cchanging injuries after crash
OL,6,FTwo occupants of the Peugeot - two
OL,7,Fwomen in their late teens - were both
OL,8,Ffound to have sustained life-changing
OL,9,Finjuries and were taken to hospital,
OL,10,Fwhere they both remain.
OL,12,FThe person in the Citroen suffered
OL,13,Fminor injuries.
OL,15,FA section of the road was closed for
OL,16,Fseveral hours while police carried out
OL,17,Finvestigations, it has since fully
OL,18,Freopened.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
