OL,3,CTwo young women left with life-
OL,4,Cchanging injuries after crash
OL,6,FNorthumbria Police are keen to hear
OL,7,Ffrom any witnesses, particularly
OL,8,Fanyone who saw the moments leading up
OL,9,Fto the collision, or anyone travelling
OL,10,Fin the area at the time who has
OL,11,Fdashcam footage.
OL,13,FAnyone able to help the investigation
OL,14,Fis being urged to contact the force
OL,15,Fvia their website or by calling 101.
